@startuml Sequence_User_Management

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "User API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

== View Profile ==
User -> Client: Access profile page
Client -> API: GET /api/users/profile
API -> API: Verify token
API -> DB: Get user data
DB --> API: User profile
API --> Client: Return profile
Client --> User: Display profile

== Update Profile ==
User -> Client: Edit profile info
Client -> API: PUT /api/users/profile
API -> API: Validate data
API -> DB: Update user
DB --> API: User updated
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show success

== Admin Manage Sellers ==
User -> Client: View sellers list
Client -> API: GET /api/admin/sellers
API -> DB: Get sellers list
DB --> API: Sellers data
API --> Client: Return sellers
Client --> User: Display sellers

User -> Client: Approve seller
Client -> API: POST /api/admin/sellers/:id/approve
API -> DB: Update seller status
DB --> API: Seller approved
API --> Client: Success response

== Admin Manage Customers ==
User -> Client: View customers list
Client -> API: GET /api/admin/customers
API -> DB: Get customers
DB --> API: Customers data
API --> Client: Return customers
Client --> User: Display customers

@enduml

